It~would be~nice if everybody will consider Luwrain just as~an~attempt to~create something new,
hopefully, interesting and useful in~areas, which previously didn't get enough attention.
Besides that, me is very grateful to~all [[http://emacspeak.sourceforge.net  emacspeak]] authors 
